# OPNsense

This file contains the deployment, configuration, networking, and troubleshooting documentation for the OPNsense firewall used in the SOC homelab environment.

## Topics Covered
- Initial installation and persistence setup
- VirtualBox network architecture
- WAN/LAN interface configuration
- DHCP and routing validation
- Internal network segmentation
- Future integrations such as IDS/IPS, proxy filtering, HA, CARP, and pfSync

## Current Status
- OPNsense installed successfully
- UFS configured on virtual disk
- Persistent boot issue resolved
- LAN configured as 10.200.200.254/24
- Internal Network established using VirtualBox Intnet

## Notes
This firewall serves as the central gateway and security control point for the SOC homelab environment.
